comments: Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact to Gallinari's (OKC) front as he gathers the ball on his driving shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) extends his forearm into Schroder's (OKC) body and initiates contact that affects his ability to maintain his defensive position.
Paul (OKC) makes marginal contact with Lowry (TOR) after he releases his shot attempt as Lowry is jumping away from Paul.
Powell (TOR) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Schroder (OKC) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Muscala (OKC) establishes and maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Lowry (TOR).
Paul (OKC) extends two hands into Lowry's (TOR) back and affects his ability to rebound.
Muscala (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position on Anunoby (TOR) on the end of the drive.
Paul (OKC) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Muscala (OKC) makes marginal contact with Powell (TOR) at the start of the drive.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Patton (OKC).
